    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing reliable transportation. Mechanically, it remains sound and starts up without issue, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. It has been regularly serviced to ensure it stays roadworthy, making it a practical choice for a daily driver or a first car for a student.",
