    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This specimen has been curated with meticulous attention to its mechanical performance and remains in a state of commendable preservation. Featuring a robust powertrain and a well-appointed interior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning motorist. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a history of consistent upkeep, ensuring its next steward a seamless transition into high-caliber ownership.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
