      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s super reliable for daily commutes or fun weekend trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a robust 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six (N54) mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity and has been maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, including a recently refreshed cooling system and high-pressure fuel pump. The rear-wheel-drive configuration is enhanced by a limited-slip differential, providing superior turn-in and corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with spirited use, the suspension geometry remains true, featuring upgraded polyurethane bushings and adjustable coilovers for a dialed-in damping profile. A perfect candidate for a purist seeking a mechanically sound platform with peak boost pressure holding steady across the rev range.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
