      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i in Black Sapphire Metallic. This vehicle has been garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly, preserving a deep, mirror-like finish on the exterior. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving, the body is free of dents or significant scratches. Inside, the Canberra Beige Dakota leather interior is in excellent shape; the seats remain firm and supple, and the cabin is strictly non-smoking with no pet odors. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, Harman Kardon premium audio, and navigation system, function perfectly. Mechanically, this X5 is robust. It comes with a complete service history, having recently undergone a full inspection, oil service, and brake pad replacement. The tires currently show approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a turn-key luxury SUV that offers a smooth, quiet ride and a commanding presence on the road. Clear title in hand.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
